# Iact3 Action
[![GitHub Marketplace](https://img.shields.io/badge/Marketplace-Iact3%20Action-blue.svg?colorA=24292e&colorB=0366d6&style=flat&longCache=true&logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://github.com/marketplace/actions/create-issue-from-file)

`Iact3 Action`是针对阿里云ROS模板仓库[ros-templates](https://github.com/aliyun/ros-templates)的专用Github Action。用于测试合并至仓库的ROS模板是否可以成功部署。
